Record Class Profile

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Record
com.stag.identity.person.model.Profile
Record Components:
personId - the person ID
studentIds - the list of student IDs associated with the person
firstName - the first name
lastName - the last name
birthSurname - the birth surname
contact - contact information
titles - academic and professional titles
birthNumber - the birth number
birthDate - the birthdate
birthPlace - birthplace information
citizenship - citizenship information
passportNumber - the passport number
gender - the gender
maritalStatus - the marital status
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public record Profile(Integer personId, List<String> studentIds, String firstName, String lastName, String birthSurname, Profile.Contact contact, Profile.Titles titles, String birthNumber, LocalDate birthDate, Profile.BirthPlace birthPlace, Profile.Citizenship citizenship, String passportNumber, String gender, String maritalStatus) extends Record implements Serializable

Profile Model

Complete person profile containing personal information, contact details, citizenship, and associated student IDs. Used for full profile retrieval with localized codelist meanings.

Version:
1.0.0
Author:
Jakub Pavlíček
